{"tid":218794,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"[長文]彩拉麵真係咁好食？","createTime":"2017-04-26T17:33:52.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-01T14:51:53.000Z","uid":1858,"like":4,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"afd4174f5691aa5c57bf90afcb09d115f1ec3af3","tid":218794,"uid":1858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T17:33:52.000Z","msg":"話說小弟今日去開元朗，就試下呢間比人講到天上有地下冇嘅沾麵鋪。<br />\n<br />\n事關我食晚市，都算係頭個批客，完全唔洗等。<br />\n但係我一去到條巷仔到就已經聞到好大陣好多烈嘅尿壓味，入到鋪頭亦都好焗，有陣up味好唔舒服，要坐左幾分鐘先適應到（有諗過走，差d頂唔順）<br />\n<br />\n叫完野食，d野都算黎得快，我就叫左個黑油沾麵，食落就真係冇預期咁好食（可能太多人捧）<br />\nD叉燒亦同我印象嘅日叉有分別，出面d日法會傾向汁味重d ，佢呢款就反而係肉味出d,特別係額外加個碟，因為佢另上，就算放d叉燒入湯到都唔係索到好多味。<br />\n<br />\n總括黎講，間野主環扣分位都係環境方面，野食我就覺得叫中中挺挺<br />\n<br />\n利申：平時少食亦唔多鐘意食日本野，所以唔識太多銷頭，比較唔到"},{"pid":"6a559174273fd3d821fe7c7152a2d789b657a0f9","tid":218794,"uid":1858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T17:36:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>話說小弟今日去開元朗，就試下呢間比人講到天上有地下冇嘅沾麵鋪。<br />\n<br />\n事關我食晚市，都算係頭個批客，所以完全唔洗等。<br />\n但係我一去到條巷仔到就已經聞到好大陣好強烈嘅尿壓味，入到鋪頭亦都好焗，有陣up味好唔舒服，要坐左幾分鐘先適應到（有諗過走，差d頂唔順）<br />\n<br />\n叫完野食，d野都算黎得快，我就叫左個黑油沾麵，食落就真係冇預期咁好食（可能太多人捧）<br />\nD叉燒亦同我印象嘅日叉有分別，出面d日叉會傾向汁味重d ，佢呢款就反而係肉味出d,特別係額外加個碟，因為佢另上，就算放d叉燒入湯到都唔係索到好多味。<br />\n<br />\n總括黎講，間野主要扣分位都係環境方面，野食我就覺得叫中中挺挺<br />\n<br />\n利申：平時少食亦唔多鐘意食日本野，所以唔識太多銷頭，比較唔到</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好多錯字，自膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfbf6c3dc3c5d35afb46821e039c13570f026fc2","tid":218794,"uid":93900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T17:38:51.000Z","msg":"好食 完"},{"pid":"0403f14d051743397ae19b9460caba7f6b9d6f97","tid":218794,"uid":4210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T17:39:25.000Z","msg":"直接講最尾嗰句咪得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13d107e7e555149dc1eecb4c5d59f26f1cceb6a0","tid":218794,"uid":1858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T17:40:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好食 完</blockquote><br />\n其實我有懷疑係咪我去錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n間野係個益中心後面架麻<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n同埋可能我平時食日本拉麵都鐘意食辣味，佢個到好似冇，所以唔多啱心水"},{"pid":"07ae02a808f14ddc0735d8deedc62e9c485f4b55","tid":218794,"uid":1858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T17:42:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>直接講最尾嗰句咪得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06c1800dbbeed6ef5627e5752d0c0adeee977e77","tid":218794,"uid":20856,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T18:02:50.000Z","msg":"佢個麵幼身咗啲，但幾香，應該就係你所講嘅尿味，其實差不多間間拉麵舖都有呢浸除<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n最近食過，只能講唔太啱自己口味，因為我鍾意周月嗰種酸嘅沾麵多啲，彩嗰個我要落佢個醋先啱食。去開嗰頭可以試吓，香港嚟講算唔錯，只係口味唔係我鍾意嗰款咁解。"},{"pid":"0c4269f1d72a56c5cc14247e1200979d687e4181","tid":218794,"uid":1858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T18:05:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>佢個麵幼身咗啲，但幾香，應該就係你所講嘅尿味，其實差不多間間拉麵舖都有呢浸除<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n最近食過，只能講唔太啱自己口味，因為我鍾意周月嗰種酸嘅沾麵多啲，彩嗰個我要落佢個醋先啱食。去開嗰頭可以試吓，香港嚟講算唔錯，只係口味唔係我鍾意嗰款咁解。</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 原來係佢d麵味黎<br />\n<br />\n長知識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n可能我同巴打一樣唔太食得慣<br />\n<br />\n巴打有冇邊間平時食開覺得好正<br />\n比我參考下"},{"pid":"5225385340f8011292208bf3c66855ba4227ae95","tid":218794,"uid":10788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T18:05:42.000Z","msg":"元朗山上先好食"},{"pid":"74310a60f79eb877ef42029b89be746964da83e4","tid":218794,"uid":1858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T18:12:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>元朗山上先好食</blockquote><br />\nSearch 左Google map 係咪地山謙，但係暫時結業wo<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5c72f453dbd83dec1aea088b922de2da1b7196c","tid":218794,"uid":27665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T18:23:29.000Z","msg":"應該講山下"},{"pid":"e435d2e517f27c87eeccf2a63f4c280a3556c18a","tid":218794,"uid":78039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T18:26:20.000Z","msg":"我覺得係果浸肉腥味，應該係煲湯果陣臭味，上次去我都聞到好臭想走"},{"pid":"370f2705406ed64cc8792692876866106691e42e","tid":218794,"uid":15921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T18:30:59.000Z","msg":"彩就算中上啦，唔算特別好食<br />\n隱家我最鍾意"},{"pid":"4b52b1926a073b01dd15d418fcea125860842980","tid":218794,"uid":1858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T19:34:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>應該講山下</blockquote><br />\n山下就搵到"},{"pid":"d2be6e652a129a827832c03ff19eb95b5f9d10e6","tid":218794,"uid":1858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T19:35:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我覺得係果浸肉腥味，應該係煲湯果陣臭味，上次去我都聞到好臭想走</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我入到去頂左幾分鐘見開始適應左先冇走"},{"pid":"fccbc05b0873804ba9a9fecee8a63a473e255817","tid":218794,"uid":1858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T19:36:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>彩就算中上啦，唔算特別好食<br />\n隱家我最鍾意</blockquote><br />\n下次去試下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n雖然少食同唔多鐘意食日本野。但係都鐘意好食嘅拉麵"},{"pid":"69ca72f29bf2a52d60db77bd8e285c4d4c56140b","tid":218794,"uid":23954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T19:45:48.000Z","msg":"真係咁好食"},{"pid":"6ec70602f1e193254723c774d9bd5bafaedce618","tid":218794,"uid":1858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T01:14:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e31af049ed04675e8c4f575e7c785faf46a7dd6","tid":218794,"uid":77092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T01:15:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2eae65e1a7f598b6887535c99c592e86a8ab53f9","tid":218794,"uid":11977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T03:46:18.000Z","msg":"人地蝦湯出名<br />\n你食黑油唔好食就問點解吹捧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n可以話彩係值8x蚊 唔貴 而且元朗冇乜拉麵鋪 所以先比較突出"},{"pid":"7f5cc70ced782760bbf2ae02b39e08bf3d4c40ec","tid":218794,"uid":31,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T03:49:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>人地蝦湯出名<br />\n你食黑油唔好食就問點解吹捧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n可以話彩係值8x蚊 唔貴 而且元朗冇乜拉麵鋪 所以先比較突出</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n連人地出名咩都唔知就出文唱鳩人 樓主ho ball<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70d302cb83c955027c525f51c95c43f1996dd04d","tid":218794,"uid":87215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T03:50:37.000Z","msg":"唔好低能啦你地，果陣尿壓味係鮮荀味黎，咩味都唔知就學人出食評。<br />\n不過我食過一次都覺得普通，仲要排隊冇下次"},{"pid":"be8d6af7cebaff74b445fbe1aa655f84db57833a","tid":218794,"uid":87215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T03:52:56.000Z","msg":"有間隱世拉麵以前係元朗依家搬左去屯門青菱虹橋果到，呢間拉麵就真係好食，好食過彩"},{"pid":"2ca9c157d0fd759a5d81290aced5699d0ecb4222","tid":218794,"uid":51121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T04:00:12.000Z","msg":"我覺得拉面只有好食同唔好食, 但就無超好食."},{"pid":"0b05ce2dfd094deb04722ae6650e1d016af8f451","tid":218794,"uid":66129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T04:01:42.000Z","msg":"彩同屯門嗰間赤橋都係有陣尿壓味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔知佢地加咗乜咁臭"},{"pid":"cffd825398fd75147fb8791935a5bfc48bedcc9d","tid":218794,"uid":58622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T04:02:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有間隱世拉麵以前係元朗依家搬左去屯門青菱虹橋果到，呢間拉麵就真係好食，好食過彩</blockquote><br />\n我隱你老母咩"},{"pid":"94bbddf14de343726740a14f31234653bb97854b","tid":218794,"uid":87215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T04:04:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>彩同屯門嗰間赤橋都係有陣尿壓味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔知佢地加咗乜咁臭</blockquote><br />\n都話係鮮荀"},{"pid":"b1fe9c376a02e1f50c9a6c7b1d2051814ba4919d","tid":218794,"uid":87215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T04:04:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有間隱世拉麵以前係元朗依家搬左去屯門青菱虹橋果到，呢間拉麵就真係好食，好食過彩</blockquote><br />\n我隱你老母咩</blockquote><br />\n？？"},{"pid":"fe2ad85151c29770dc1f8036f741e1ff9d8001aa","tid":218794,"uid":2772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T04:15:39.000Z","msg":"需知道吹捧既人都係鄉下仔...鄉下仔話好食<br />\n而你又真係信<br />\n咁係智慧問題"},{"pid":"4c156fe3a2dd5eb0bf300d179660d7671b0a35e4","tid":218794,"uid":12618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T04:38:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>有間隱世拉麵以前係元朗依家搬左去屯門青菱虹橋果到，呢間拉麵就真係好食，好食過彩</blockquote><br />\n我隱你老母咩</blockquote><br />\n？？</blockquote><br />\n赤橋食過一次 我唔會再食<br />\n個湯連暖都稱唔上  淨係呢樣已經扣晒分<br />\n叉燒唔得  淨係得個面好食<br />\n個地方好焗  地下又冼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n貼錢都唔去  <br />\n暫時食過係最差既一間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7283047de0f21e1884825c2c2f70246fbf549fc","tid":218794,"uid":87215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T04:49:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>有間隱世拉麵以前係元朗依家搬左去屯門青菱虹橋果到，呢間拉麵就真係好食，好食過彩</blockquote><br />\n我隱你老母咩</blockquote><br />\n？？</blockquote><br />\n赤橋食過一次 我唔會再食<br />\n個湯連暖都稱唔上  淨係呢樣已經扣晒分<br />\n叉燒唔得  淨係得個面好食<br />\n個地方好焗  地下又冼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n貼錢都唔去  <br />\n暫時食過係最差既一間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁我又冇你呢個情況 可能我係晚市第一枱客"},{"pid":"32ec6c8853a3007df3de35309dfb9aee7f41b9b4","tid":218794,"uid":97028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T06:02:43.000Z","msg":"樓豬係咪食慣屎所以覺得彩唔好食？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1adb01ca30884d269af3a2d79e282689c2012a2","tid":218794,"uid":1858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T06:23:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係咪成班打手黎<br />\n出個食評姐，洗唔洗咁肉緊<br />\n<br />\n況且我又冇話唔好食，成班打手係咪盲，我淨係話冇預期咁好食炸wo<br />\n屌人都睇清楚先啦死盲閪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c963c6085d71c2d26e0d30f7d3b89b188b37b26c","tid":218794,"uid":1858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T06:24:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>需知道吹捧既人都係鄉下仔...鄉下仔話好食<br />\n而你又真係信<br />\n咁係智慧問題</blockquote><br />\n點知連登咁多鄉下仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aed52de8dfbeb5ef