oji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 即係假設間野好難食，但原來其他人整嘅仲難食，所以佢係好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 食得少日本野唔可以講感想？你未做過官又走去彈d官？<br />\n<br />\n同埋我利申係因為我對日本野冇乜興趣，就算食完都唔會記得間野叫咩名係邊到，我認我up唔出鋪名去比較有咩問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1bc150c23925030cfabdf785f7f08f9f6cb6de1","tid":218794,"uid":1858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T07:12:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好多打手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢地好肉緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔講以為間鋪佢地有份<br />\n<br />\n話普普通通都唔收貨"},{"pid":"da27550ffd045ac53a34103ca36218640a926cf2","tid":218794,"uid":1858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T07:13:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屯門vs元朗</blockquote><br />\n聽聞屯門個間過人一棟再加抄人<br />\n利申唔知有冇記錯，有錯屌細力d"},{"pid":"e6ae7127ad470e795a68300484bca8c6fbc6ece5","tid":218794,"uid":51250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T07:20:08.000Z","msg":"赤橋食過一次，唔掂<br />\n<br />\n未食過彩"},{"pid":"ee2cb78bee69f47840fcd1cf9e9351f8b1cb4e41","tid":218794,"uid":87215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T07:21:47.000Z","msg":"原來屯門間野同彩有牙齒印 屋唔知，有冇巴打分享多d"},{"pid":"59c983a007c37291f37ab68da1cd16e2a25f5934","tid":218794,"ui